#. plugin:vonage:summary
#: 
msgid "Vonage SMS enables text message notifications for ChurchCRM using the Vonage API (formerly Nexmo). Send SMS alerts to parents when their child checks in via the kiosk system."
msgstr "Vonage SMS 使用 Vonage API（前身為 Nexmo）為 ChurchCRM 提供簡訊通知功能。當兒童透過自助服務站系統簽到時，向家長發送 SMS 警報。"

#. plugin:vonage:section:6:content
#: 
msgid "Vonage charges per SMS sent. Pricing varies by destination country. See the Vonage pricing page for current rates. New accounts receive free trial credit for testing."
msgstr "Vonage 按發送的 SMS 收費。定價因目的地國家/地區而異。請查看 Vonage 定價頁面以了解當前費率。新帳號可獲得免費試用額度用於測試。"

